Winthorpe is a very steady young man.

107
00:13:20,925 --> 00:13:23,218
We're lucky to have him
managing ourfirm for us.

108
00:13:23,260 --> 00:13:28,223
Oh, hogwash. Exeter,
he's the product of good e

