Once you have a man with no legs,
you never go back, baby.

116
00:13:54,834 --> 00:13:57,794
I knowwhatyou're thinking.
You seen Porgy and Bess?

117
00:13:58,337 --> 00:14:00,880
We can make it, baby. Me and you.

118
00:14:02,466 --> 00:14:03,550
You bitch!

119
00:14:16,772 --> 00:14:18,314
Who's that? Who's there?
Whatyou want?

120
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:20,400
