126
00:14:33,956 --> 00:14:36,958
I was in Sang Bang, Dang Gong.

127
00:14:37,042 --> 00:14:40,211
I was all overthat place,
basically a lot of places, a lot of places.

128
00:14:40,296 --> 00:14:41,880
