138
00:15:11,952 --> 00:15:15,747
I have... Oh shit, look at this.
Man! I can walk.

139
00:15:15,831 --> 00:15:19,083
Jesus, praise Jesus.

140
00:15:19,501 --> 00:15:22,879
I appreciate this. Oh, this is beautiful.
I can't believe... Thank you.

141
00:15:22,922 --> 00:15:25,214
I just don't knowwhat to do. It's...

142
00:15:25,549 --> 00:15:29,052
Glory be to God. Praise Jesus.
Look at me.

143
00:15:29,136 --> 00:15:31,596
This is too much. I can't believe it.

144
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:33,848
You're beautiful.
Listen, I can't thank you.

145
00:15:33,891 --> 00:15:36,225
First Moses, now this. God, Jesus...

146
00:15:36,352 --> 00:15:38,686
Oh, baby, look at me.

147
00:15:38,729 --> 00:15:41,773
I'm so happy. Oh, God.
Look at me, this is too much.

148
00:15:41,857 --> 00:15:44,317
What a happy day. What a happy day!

149
00:15:44,401 --> 00:15:47,236
Really, I appreciate it, y'all.
Okay now. All right. Look at this.

150
00:15:47,321 --> 00:15:51,240
I can walk. I don't knowwhat to say.
I'll be all right. Take it easy.

151
00:15:51,575 --> 00:15:54,786
You're beautiful,
both ofyou all, the two ofyou.

152
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:05,046
How're you doing?

153
00:16:12,471 --> 00:16:14,931
-Oh, I'm sorry about that, man.
-Stop, thief.

154
00:16:15,015 --> 00:16:17,642
-Help, help!
-What are you talking about, man?

155
00:16:17,726 --> 00:16:21,396
Don't shoot. Take it, take it.
Please don't kill me. I'm getting married.

156
00:16:21,438 --> 00:16:24,732
-Hey, I don'twantyour bag, man.
-Help! Help!

157
00:16:25,943 --> 00:16:27,110
Help! Help!

158
00:16:28,362 --> 00:16:29,779
Help!

159
00:16:29,822 --> 00:16:32,240
He's in there. After him.

160
00:16:37,162 --> 00:16:40,498
-Excuse me.
-Watch out. He probably has a weapon.

161
00:16:43,210 --> 00:16:46,129
WINTHORPE: Stop him. He has
my briefcase. Stop him! Stop him!

162
00:16:46,463 --> 00:16:48,631
He's inside. That boy's crazy.

163
00:16:48,674 --> 00:16:50,508
-WINTHORPE: He's escaping. Get him.
-Shit.

164
00:16:51,010 --> 00:16:52,844
MAN 1: Look at him.
MAN 2: Get out ofthe way.

165
00:16:52,928 --> 00:16:54,929
Get him. He's getting away.

166
00:16:54,972 --> 00:16:56,973
There he is. That's him.
Get him. Get him.

167
00:16:57,057 --> 00:16:59,142
He's underthe table.
Somebody go underthere.

168
00:16:59,184 --> 00:17:00,393
Somebody get down there.

169
00:17:00,477 --> 00:17:02,770
Right there. Right there. There he is.

170
00:17:06,150 --> 00:17:08,192
Is there a problem, officers?

171
00:17:16,827 --> 00:17:19,203
What in heaven's name
is going on here?

172
00:17:19,288 --> 00:17:22,373
He tried to rob the payroll, Randolph.
He attacked me in broad daylight.

173
00:17:22,458 --> 00:17:24,584
I didn't do nothing, man.
This guy bumped into me.

174
00:17:24,668 --> 00:17:27,462
I did not. You knocked me down
and tried to grab my briefcase.

175
00:17:27,504 --> 00:17:30,465
-Yeah, but itwas an accident, man.
-An accident, really?

176
00:17:30,507 --> 00:17:32,008
What's going to happen to this man?

177
00:17:32,051 --> 00:17:33,176
We're gonna book him

178
00:17:33,218 --> 00:17:36,471
on assault, attempted robbery
and resisting arrest.

179
00:17:37,014 --> 00:17:38,723
Well done, Winthorpe.

180
00:17:38,807 --> 00:17:40,641
Hey, man, I'm innocent.
This guy bumped into me.

181
00:17:40,684 --> 00:17:42,810
I was trying to give him his briefcase
back to him.

182
00:17:42,853 --> 00:17:43,895
Shit, I can't be going tojail

183
00:17:43,979 --> 00:17:45,813
'cause some asswipe ain'twatching
where he's going.

184
00:17:45,856 --> 00:17:48,691
Officer, I would like to press
full charges.

185
00:17:48,776 --> 00:17:51,527
People like this are
a menace to decent society.

186
