You have a history ofjuvenile arrests,
I presume?

189
00:17:59,369 --> 00:18:02,663
Drug abuse, reform school,
state prisons and all that?

190
00:18:02,706 --> 00:18:04,582
I ain't talking to this guy.
I want a lawyer.

191
00:18:04,666 --> 00:18:06,667
Is there a lawyer in the house?

192
00:18:06,710 --> 00:18:07,710
(CLEARS THROAT)

193
00:18:13,050 --> 00:18:16,177
That man is a product
of a poor environment.

194
00:18:16,303 --> 00:18:18,971
There's absolutely nothing wrong
with him, I can prove it.

195
00:18:19,056 --> 00:18:22,100
Of course there's
something wrong with him.

196
00:18:22,184 --> 00:18:24,227
He's a Negro!

