with me, Miss Penelope.

226
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:28,601
You're so hot-tempered, darling.

227
00:20:30,979 --> 00:20:34,148
I would have groveled on the ground
and begged for mercy.

228
00:20:41,907 --> 00:20:44,116
